Member of the Month



















July 2017: Frank Schuler

Frank Schuler's recognition as Member of the Month is long overdue. With more than 100 blogs and approximately double that amount of questions (since the SAP Community launched in October 2016), Frank has built quite a reputation -- with more than 100 followers relying on his expertise.




View interview


View profile

















June 2017: Akhilesh Upadhyay

Akhilesh Upadhyay has answered more than 150 questions in SAP Community -- and that number climbs on a daily basis. An expert in SAP UI5 and Fiori app development, Akhilesh has made it clear that members can call on his knowledge -- both inside and outside of SAP Community.




View interview


View profile

















May 2017: Koen Hesters

Koen Hesters has been a community member for 3 years, and while that may seem like a short span of time compared to other Member of the Month winners, the entrepreneur behind a "one-man show" has accomplished a lot in a little time: 30 badges, nearly as many blog posts, dozens of followers, and 100 questions answered this year alone.




View interview


View profile

















April 2017: Jun Wu

Jun Wu is the Member of the Month for April 2017. With more than 170 followers and more than 330 answers since launch, he has spent approximately a decade establishing himself as an expert and a valuable source of information for SAP Community members.




View interview


View profile













